{"tid":2231774,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"SpaceX的SN7.1「成功爆炸」 SN8 要接著試飛了","createTime":"2020-10-06T02:08:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-06T12:34:23.000Z","uid":295230,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"46a41be28855d5029829b6de89240a9e4a331dda","tid":2231774,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T02:08:55.000Z","msg":"馬斯克 SpaceX 又爆炸了，但這次是<strong>故意爆炸</strong>，目的是了解和研究 304L 不鏽鋼燃料箱能承受的壓力極限，同時也為 SN8 試飛做準備。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>終於測試成功！SN7.1 成功爆炸，SN8 要接著試飛了</strong><br />\n<br />\n經過 92 小時測試後，太空梭原型機 SN7.1 終於成功爆炸。但這次是故意爆炸，目的是了解和研究 304L 不鏽鋼燃料箱能承受的壓力極限，同時也為 SN8 試飛做準備。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CkFFgngw6Q4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DCkFFgngw6Q4&d=SBcu0iNh8WN0EYdC3CIZL6DCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=322ea8c3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CkFFgngw6Q4</a><br />\n<br />\nSN7.1 是個測試儲罐，不是完整的太空梭原型機，主要測試採用新材料的耐壓情況。換句話說，SN7.1 就是做來測試極限的，測試到爆炸為止，才能知道極限耐壓值是多少。SN7.1 其實已多次測試，包括低溫測試等，但結果並沒有透露太多。但據外媒稱，SpaceX 對穹蓋、焊縫、架構等各部位受力情況都進行過嚴密測試，取得詳細的實驗參數。<br />\n<br />\nSN7.1 測試成功也意味 SN8 將嘗試首次試飛。如果試飛成功，這將刷新航空紀錄。畢竟，這可是高達 50 公尺、直徑 9 公尺、重達幾百噸、推力多達 600 多噸的怪獸，要想演出最高飛行高度 20 公里的空氣動力學航空之旅，絕非易事。<br />\n<br />\n據馬斯克介紹，與「無頭」SN5、SN6 版不同，<strong>SN8 將是接近最終型的太空梭</strong>，除了內部和發動機，外形架構已是最終版。且與 SN5、SN6 離開地面的測試不同，<strong>SN8 要飛到 18 公里高，為後續星艦重返大氣層和在其他星球飛行做準備。</strong>據悉，SN8 也會經歷同樣的早期測試及靜態點火、其他地面檢查等前期準備工作，緊接是另一個最終嘗試飛到海拔 6 萬英尺高空，並回到地面完成控制著陸前的靜態點火測試。<br />\n<br />\n據 SpaceX 最近提交聯邦通訊委員會（FCC）的檔案，希望 10 月 11 日後某個時間試飛。如果成功，意味我們離太空旅遊的夢想又近了一步。除 SN8 外，目前 Spacex 建造中的還有 SN9、SN10、SN11 三艘原型機。按照計劃，<strong>距離真正建造完成星際火箭 Starship 還需更新到 SN20，都要在 3 年內完成。</strong>"},{"pid":"1fd703d9f6c7c17e961d9166ed77542cb2771e95","tid":2231774,"uid":294518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T02:11:22.000Z","msg":"科學大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1300a92e07171dd4b0d84fb9186cf4576b6a169","tid":2231774,"uid":59522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T02:17:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f393991a34560381f7fdf89ecfc68c73daf38df4","tid":2231774,"uid":47309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T04:36:18.000Z","msg":"太空時代<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e325c0f68faf9fdd8b45e2088af94ce53c51675","tid":2231774,"uid":44454,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T04:39:03.000Z","msg":"呢一個步驟， 中國晨早試咗啦， 垃撚圾"},{"pid":"e7a2e70c1fa3ca86f5c8daca6d79b1a21a6ce0b3","tid":2231774,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e325c0f68faf9fdd8b45e2088af94ce53c51675","tid":2231774,"uid":44454,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T04:39:03.000Z","msg":"呢一個步驟， 中國晨早試咗啦， 垃撚圾"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T11:50:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa7fa7cad3feb24b74b03cea9e35937513cf6d8d","tid":2231774,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e325c0f68faf9fdd8b45e2088af94ce53c51675","tid":2231774,"uid":44454,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T04:39:03.000Z","msg":"呢一個步驟， 中國晨早試咗啦， 垃撚圾"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T12:00:53.000Z","msg":"爆到渣都冇淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/n